          <.heading2 margin="my-5" id="table-space">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/table/#table-space"}>
              Space prop in Phoenix LiveView table content Component
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The space prop only is applicable on
            <.custom_inline_code>separated</.custom_inline_code>
            variant.
            The space prop offers values like <.custom_inline_code>extra_small</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>small</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>medium</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>large</.custom_inline_code>, and <.custom_inline_code>extra_large</.custom_inline_code>.
          </.cp>

