          <.heading2 margin="my-5" id="table-pagination">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/table/#table-pagination"}>
              Use Mishka Chelekom pagination with tables
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The
            <.custom_inline_code>pagination</.custom_inline_code>
            component can be used with the
            <.custom_inline_code>table</.custom_inline_code>
            component for efficient pagination of table data, allowing users to navigate through large datasets easily.
          </.cp>

          <.custom_block position="left" color="success" class="my-8" border="medium">
            <.cp>
              You can use the
              <.link
                class="text-emerald-700 font-semibold"
                patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/pagination"}
                title="Mishka Chelekom pagination component"
              >
                Mishka Chelekom pagination component
              </.link>
              with the table component to efficiently navigate through large datasets.
            </.cp>
          </.custom_block>

          <.custom_code_wrapper code_class="text-xs" elements_class="space-y-5">
            <.table
              header_border="extra_small"
